p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;This idea of questioning things that hitherto you thought were unassailable in a particular domain is really interesting.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
